<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Bantuan</strong>
Selamat datang di beranda aplikasi mugee</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-616" src="http://cipiyoh.com/mugee/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/beranda-218x300.png" alt="" width="218" height="300" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Apabila anda sudah punya akun silahkan login langsung, dan apabila belum silahkan klik "DAFTAR SEKARANG"</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">
<img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-617" src="http://cipiyoh.com/mugee/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/halaman-login-194x300.png" alt="" width="194" height="300" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Masukkan identitas anda pada form yang sudah disediakan, kemudian klik "DAFTAR"</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-618" src="http://cipiyoh.com/mugee/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/form-biodata-176x300.png" alt="" width="176" height="300" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Ini merupakan contoh profil apabila anda sudah register dan login</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-619" src="http://cipiyoh.com/mugee/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/profil-pengguna-194x300.png" alt="" width="194" height="300" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Apabila ingin mengganti password anda bisa klik "GANTI PASSWORD"</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-620" src="http://cipiyoh.com/mugee/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/keluar-192x300.png" alt="" width="192" height="300" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Silahkan masukkan password lama anda kemudian password baru dan ulangi lalu klik "SIMPAN"</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-624" src="http://cipiyoh.com/mugee/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/ubah-password-245x300.png" alt="" width="245" height="300" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Apabila anda lupa password klik "LUPA PASSWORD" pada halaman login dan masukkan email anda kemudian "SUBMIT"</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-617" src="http://cipiyoh.com/mugee/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/halaman-login-194x300.png" alt="" width="194" height="300" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-626" src="http://cipiyoh.com/mugee/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/lupaa-password-215x300.png" alt="" width="215" height="300" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Anda juga bisa memberikan feedback kepada kami</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-620" src="http://cipiyoh.com/mugee/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/keluar-192x300.png" alt="" width="192" height="300" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-625" src="http://cipiyoh.com/mugee/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/feedback-193x300.png" alt="" width="193" height="300" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">jika sudah selesai menggunakan akun anda silahkan "KELUAR" supaya akun anda tidak disalah gunakan</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-620" src="http://cipiyoh.com/mugee/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/keluar-192x300.png" alt="" width="192" height="300" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"></p>